Edge Cases Handled

Edge Case                                 How It's Handled

Company doesn't exist                     Returns 404 before running the heavy query
Invalid company_id (string, negative)     Returns 400 with clear message
Product has no linked supplier            Returns supplier: null instead of crashing
Product has stock but zero recent sales   Excluded from alerts (not "active")
Current stock is 0 (complete stockout)    Still included — days_until_stockout will be 0
Product exists in multiple warehouses     Each warehouse gets its own alert row
Bundle products                           Explicitly excluded — component alerts handle this
Database connection failure               try/catch returns 500, client always released in finally
